ðŸ’¡ Key Design Principles
Progressive Disclosure: Show complexity gradually based on role

Contextual Help: Role-specific guidance at point of need

Permission Clarity: Always show why something is disabled

Role Switching: Easy to switch perspectives when wearing multiple hats

Training Integration: Role-specific learning paths built into workflow

This role architecture ensures each user gets exactly what they need, nothing more, nothing less. The platform feels like it was custom-built for their specific job function while maintaining enterprise consistency and security.